abstract: Poughkeepsie, NY, police say body recovered from Hudson River is not that of Vincent Viafore, man who prosecutors contend was killed by his fiancee Angelika Graswald.
lead_paragraph: Investigators said on Thursday that the body of a man found near Poughkeepsie, N.Y., is not that of Vincent Viafore, 46, who prosecutors say was killed by his fiancée.

headline.main: Body Found in Hudson River Is Not Missing Kayaker, Police Say
headline.print_headline: Officials Say Body Is Not of Kayaker
